<br>
&quot;I have tried to teach you the way. I have been patient up until now.&quot; A dark light flashed in Arikel's eyes. &quot;I will not guide you through life anymore, Zariel&quot;, he said flatly as he started to exit the arena. &quot;You're on your own now.&quot;<br>
<br>
