<br>
&quot;What's going on?&quot; she thought. &quot;Setis and Laocoon have gone mad, Eltherion has died, and now my brother has been changed.&quot;<br>
Zariel laid on the arena floor, trying to hold together her world as it crumbled apart.<br>
